ed features and maintain only one file. Additionally, updating reachability metadata seems unrelated to my current context. I just need to keep everything concise and make sure there's no need to run anything right now.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented comprehensive Scala tests for `io.circe:circe-generic_3:0.14.12` in:\n\n- `tests/src/io.circe/circe-generic_3/0.14.12/src/test/scala/io_circe/circe_generic_3/Circe_generic_3Test.scala`\n\nCoverage added for:\n\n- Semi-automatic product codec derivation with nested case classes\n- `Encoder.AsObject` composition via `JsonObject`\n- Field-level decoding failures\n- Accumulating decoder failures\n- Parameterized product derivation\n- Sealed trait hierarchy derivation\n- Automatic derivation via `io.circe.generic.auto.*`\n\nNo reachability metadata or build files were modified. Per instruction, I did not compile or run the tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_05a67a464e7b2a8c016a28dbc3345081978af2770fa626d510\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3330, "output": 675, "cacheRead": 35840, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 39845, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781062578867, "responseId": "resp_05a67a464e7b2a8c016a28dbb359308197b4e4e057ff83734d"}}
